'''Norello''' was the captain of the freighter ''[[Happer's Way]]'', out of [[Chandrila/Legends|Chandrila]]. He was contracted by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Imperial Army/Legends|Army]] to bring fifty [[All Terrain Scout Transport/Legends|AT-ST]] [[Walker/Legends|walkers]] to the garrison on [[Llorkan]], but was interrupted in his delivery by an attack from the pirate ship ''[[Cavalcade]]''. The captain and his ship were rescued by [[Emperor's Hand/Legends|Emperor's Hand]] [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]].

